{"tid":1585011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中post] 922和你Stuck4.0 賽前討論","createTime":"2019-09-21T11:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T04:15:20.000Z","uid":167548,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e09937c5db4fdd7f2250a5fbdf4c435b77fd61c5","tid":1585011,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">機鐵預計</span></em></strong><br />\n第一時間青衣 100% 封站, 提早封站<br />\n第二時間東涌 100% 封站, 不過應該是開賽之後 (鳩拉填數)<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n個人主張玩爆青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔建議勇武撚入東涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最緊要小心啊, 馬路如虎口, 班藍絲公路車撚死你唔洗陪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但是你地用雜物阻塞(<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好玩陰, 我地唔好要出人命</span>), 佢唔停就抵佢死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過講明堵橋唔一定真是是條橋上面, 可以圈圈附近馬路玩, 等班狗自已幫手封<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面圈唔是叫你搭鐵(和理非限定), 因為一定抽查細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於和理非你地就是橋橋附近社區鳩行(人多就逼出馬路, 就唔好啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMcX5F6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMcX5F6.png&h=c6d38368&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n利申上述只是本人意見, 呂麗巴是大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後提提大家留力, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>下星期日9.29 全球反共大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"249a8e996417597776b4b0e40c4a45c26e1467fd","tid":1585011,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b876ce0390b2dddaaa04714f17532fca84a95ba","tid":1585011,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"a06de0f1d04047059ccf4f1b0ce14f4f19994281","tid":1585011,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f73ab4674160251f352da6ad01f6843603f6b6","tid":1585011,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a26c62ac8147d16b7cd77823d102194e07a6b25","tid":1585011,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88f73ab4674160251f352da6ad01f6843603f6b6","tid":1585011,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:05:21.000Z","msg":"有黨鐵驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3f22f34d8406db96c3c16672a98498f1cf9118","tid":1585011,"uid":73157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:44:13.000Z","msg":"今日中午開始梅窩發現大量狗隻，到依家仍未散去<br />\n<img sr